      "span_text": "In fact, a 2006 study presented at the American Medical Informatics Association annual symposium showed that 92% of physicians access a targeted site rather than utilize a search engine (such as Google) to gather medical information  , revealing the healthy skepticism of the reliability of the average search engine to provide accurate information.",
